Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:09.91,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:245370,249916}She's the one who asked Ayuhara not to stop volleyball and come back to the team.{NOTE:早川は鮎原にバレーを捨てるなんてコートに帰ってくれと言った本人です。}
