Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:32.56,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:808474,812562}If the ball really did vanish,\Nit's a miracle brought upon by Tsutomu-kun!{NOTE:もしボールが消えたのならそれは努くんが見せてくれた奇跡なのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:36.06,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:814147,816065}Telling me to reproduce that is insensible.{NOTE:それを再現しろなんて酷いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.35,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:816065,817358}It's heartless!{NOTE:酷すぎるわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:38.31,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:817358,818318}Kozue!{NOTE:こずえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:40.98,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:819360,820987}Ah, it went in!{NOTE:はっ！やられちゃった！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:44.78,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:822488,824782}All right, it's a tie!{NOTE:よし！未だもXXXだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:47.16,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:824782,827160}Fujimi and Tenryū both have 16 points.\NContinue!{NOTE:富士見・天竜とも十六点だ！続けろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:55.50,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:831497,835501}Here, Oonuma-san…\NOonuma-san muttered to me…{NOTE:ここで大沼さんが…大沼が私に囁いたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:57.37,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:835501,837378}"Leave it to us and go to the hospital."{NOTE:「後は任して、病院へ行け」って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:02.84,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:841716,842842}I'll succeed.{NOTE:必ず勝つ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:06.05,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:842842,846054}Tsutomu-kun, please wait for me.{NOTE:努くん。それまで待ってて。お願い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.76,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:846054,847764}We won't lose to Fujimi High!{NOTE:富士見高校なんかに負けないわよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847764,848806}Go back!{NOTE:XXXだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.55,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:848806,849557}Okay!{NOTE:任して！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:10.60,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:849557,850600}One!{NOTE:ほら、ワン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.47,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:850600,851476}Two!{NOTE:ツー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.68,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:851476,852685}Three!{NOTE:スリー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:13.39,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:852685,853394}One!{NOTE:ワン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:14.43,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:853394,854437}Two!{NOTE:ツー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:15.22,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:854437,855229}Three!{NOTE:スリー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:17.98,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:855938,857982}Now! Oonuma takes over!{NOTE:ここだ！大沼が広う！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:18.56,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:857982,858566}Got it!{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:20.52,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:858566,860526}Hayakawa – spike!{NOTE:早川のスパイク！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:22.94,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:860526,862945}If it scores, Kozue can go!{NOTE:これは決めれば、こずえは病院へ行ける！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:26.40,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:864238,866407}And now, the climax of that game!{NOTE:二部だ！この試合の再現！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:28.95,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:867617,868951}Tsutomu-kun!{NOTE:努くん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.76,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:892308,894769}Kozue. You did it. You did it!{NOTE:こずえ。やった。やったのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:38.68,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:935476,938688}You died in that moment.{NOTE:この瞬間にあなたは死んでいったのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:43.48,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:938688,943484}You passed away during that attack.{NOTE:私のアタックがあなたの命の行ったっきりはなしてしまった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:44.65,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:943484,944652}Tsutomu-kun…{NOTE:努くん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:02.42,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:960501,962420}Let me share what I think.{NOTE:じゃあ、私の考えを言おう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:14.55,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:970636,974557}Vanishing attack is a special case of the double attack.{NOTE:消えるアタックはダブルアタックにおける極めて特殊な例だった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:20.89,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:974557,980897}The fact that we discovered it in the last moment of the final with Tenryū was very favorable.{NOTE:それがダブルアタック感性途上の天龍コートの決勝で現れたのは一概に奇跡とは言えない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:22.89,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:980897,982899}Ichinose-kun protected you.{NOTE:一ノ瀬くんが守ってくれたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:29.03,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:984400,989030}The reason why it worked is that we still haven't fully developed the double attack.{NOTE:なぜならダブルアタックは未だ型にはまっていない攻撃方法だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:29.98,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:989030,989989}Listen well.{NOTE:いいか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:32.82,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:989989,992825}At that time, Ayuhara was extremely confused.{NOTE:その時に鮎原は不幸にも精神的に乱れていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:38.12,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:994994,998122}But that worked to our favor.{NOTE:がそれがダブルアタックには幸いしたのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:43.46,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:998122,1003461}Ayuhara's confusion caused her to change the attack pattern before it settled in for good.{NOTE:鮎原の心理的な乱れが未だ固まっていないダブルアタックの攻撃の仕方に変化をつけてくれた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:45.17,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003461,1005171}That's how the vanishing attack was born.{NOTE:それがあの消えるアタックと成ったんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:49.38,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006506,1009383}Now onto the reason why the ball disappears.{NOTE:ではなぜあのアタックは消えてしまうのだ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:51.80,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009383,1011802}Do you have any idea, Oonuma?{NOTE:どうだ？おい、大沼。分かるか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.13,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011802,1014138}Nothing comes to my mind at all.{NOTE:全然想像つきません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:55.84,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014138,1015848}Not even a wild guess?{NOTE:一見ありえないことでも？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:58.01,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015848,1018017}Humans are prone to optical illusions.{NOTE:人間には錯覚することがある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:17:03.52,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018017,1023523}You know how our eyes\Ndon't always see what they should.{NOTE:原因この目というやつは見てるもの全てが見えるわけじゃないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:05.65,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023523,1025650}Are you talking about a blind spot?{NOTE:盲点ですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:06.73,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025650,1026734}Yes.{NOTE:そうだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:08.36,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026734,1028361}You didn't sleep in biology classes.{NOTE:生物習ったのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:12.28,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028361,1032281}The retina of the human eye has a spot that has no optic nerves at all.{NOTE:人間の網膜には一箇所視神経の欠けた部分がある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:15.36,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032281,1035368}It's called the blind spot.{NOTE:盲点あるいはマリオット盲斑という。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:17.49,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035368,1037495}Biology, now?{NOTE:いいえ、今度は生物？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:18.78,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037495,1038788}I can't follow you anymore.{NOTE:もういけません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:19.83,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038788,1039830}{NOTE:ふふ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:24.46,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039830,1044460}Our brain works in a way that it complements what we can not see.{NOTE:普段の我々は一部分見えないところがあっても心理的にそれを補っている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:27.54,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045169,1047547}We only believe that we see it.{NOTE:それで見えているつもりでいる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:29.59,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047547,1049590}Normally it works out.{NOTE:まあ、それで結構間に合っているんだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:32.13,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049590,1052134}But that was not the case in the game against Tenryū.{NOTE:ところがあの試合ではそうはいかん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:37.01,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052134,1057014}The ball changed its direction at exactly the point where the blind spot of the entire team was.{NOTE:横から縦に飛ばしたボールの曲がり角が天龍の盲点と一致した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:39.80,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057014,1059809}That's the reason it looked as if it had disappeared.{NOTE:文字通りボールは消え失せてしまう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:42.31,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059809,1062311}But everyone looked at it.{NOTE:でも盲点は一つしかありません．}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:44.27,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062311,1064272}No one said it's easy.{NOTE:確かに条件は難しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:48.85,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064272,1068859}But when the movement changes from horizontal to vertical, the eyeball stops for a moment…{NOTE:しかし縦の動きへ変わった瞬間目玉の動きが止まって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:51.65,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068859,1071654}…and the chance that the ball gets into the blind spot is high.{NOTE:…ボールが盲点に取り込む確率は高い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:52.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071654,1072572}What's next?{NOTE:だから？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:53.78,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072572,1073781}The ball vanishes.{NOTE:二度も消えた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:56.20,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073781,1076200}Just like it did in our match against Tenryū.{NOTE:天竜の時とさっき。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:02.16,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079161,1082164}Well, that's how the vanishing attack works.{NOTE:これで消えるアタックの理由が飲み込めたの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:05.79,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082164,1085793}It also explains why Suga couldn't see it,\Nwhile it looked normal to Ayuhara.{NOTE:受けた須賀には消えたが打った鮎原には見えた理由も。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:10.38,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088045,1090381}Now that we understand the science behind it, we can practice.{NOTE:理論が分かれば、実践できるはずだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:12.00,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090381,1092008}What do you think, Ayuhara?{NOTE:どうだ？鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:13.63,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092008,1093634}Ah… Yes sir.{NOTE:あっ。はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:14.46,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093634,1094468}Great!{NOTE:よし！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:16.72,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094468,1096721}Then let's try to lock the ball in the blind spot.{NOTE:文字通り敵全員への盲点をつくんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:17.72,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096721,1097722}Got it, girls?!{NOTE:いいな、皆！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:18.88,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1097722,1098889}– Yes sir!\N– Yes sir!{NOTE:—はい！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:23.39,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100099,1103394}But it sounds tough.\NCan we really do it?{NOTE:だけどそんなXXなことが本当にできるのかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:24.93,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103394,1104937}Of course we can!{NOTE:できる、できるX！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:26.43,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104937,1106439}But it's too hard for me.{NOTE:私には危ないけどさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:30.86,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106439,1110860}But with Ayuhara Kozue, who can't miss even a millimeter, we'll be fine. Right?{NOTE:1ミリの誤差も許さない名アタッカー鮎原こずえなら…ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:50.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129754,1130755}No.{NOTE:違うわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:52.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130755,1132715}That vanishing attack was a miracle.{NOTE:あの消えるアタックは奇跡よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:55.25,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132715,1135259}Tsutomu-kun protected me.{NOTE:努くんが私を守ってくれたんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:57.25,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135259,1137259}It has nothing to do with science.{NOTE:理屈XX消えるもんじゃないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:03.80,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142683,1143809}No way!{NOTE:いいやよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:04.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143809,1144935}I can't do it!{NOTE:できないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:06.14,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144935,1146145}There's no way I can.{NOTE:できるわけないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:07.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146145,1147521}It's not science.{NOTE:理屈じゃないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:08.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147521,1148814}I can't do it!{NOTE:私はいいやよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:10.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148814,1150524}There's no way a ball can disappear.{NOTE:ボールが消えるなんてありえない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:13.15,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150524,1153152}Everyone's crazy. What are they thinking?!{NOTE:皆嘘よ。XXXよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:16.98,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153152,1156989}They expect me to repeat that miracle…\NTo repeat Tsutomu-kun's gift to me…{NOTE:奇跡をやるなんて…努くんが私にやらせたことを…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:19.49,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156989,1159492}"Do it again…"\N"Complete it…"{NOTE:「もう一度やて」…「完成させろ」なんて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:21.16,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159492,1161160}I can't do it!{NOTE:できるわけないわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:25.41,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163954,1165414}So stupid!{NOTE:馬鹿！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:26.95,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165414,1166957}Everyone's stupid!{NOTE:皆皆馬鹿だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:30.04,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167625,1170044}They think I'm some volleyball machine.{NOTE:XXアタックの機械だと思ってる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:31.87,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170044,1171879}I'm just a girl!{NOTE:私だって女の子よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:34.09,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171879,1174090}I can't… I can't do it!{NOTE:いやだ！やれないわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:36.59,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174090,1176592}There's no way I make the ball vanish!{NOTE:できないのよ、ボールを消すなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:38.34,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176592,1178344}It's insane.{NOTE:気違いたったよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:43.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182348,1183933}Tsutomu-kun…{NOTE:努くん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:45.10,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183933,1185101}Tsutomu-kun.{NOTE:努くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:46.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185101,1186394}Tsutomu-kun!{NOTE:努くん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:51.23,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189897,1191232}Tsutomu-kun!{NOTE:努くん！…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:11.37,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206205,1211377}The Yagisawa sisters of Jidōin High School. Kakinouchi from Fukuoka. Sanjou from Kanagawa.{NOTE:寺堂院の八木沢三姉妹はもちろん福岡の垣之内、神奈川の三条。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:15.00,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211377,1215005}Ayuhara-san and Hayakawa-san told me how good they were…{NOTE:この二人の強さは一緒に全日本ジュニアで戦ってきた…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.71,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215005,1217717}…when they played together in the junior national team.{NOTE:…鮎原さん、早川さんから聞いた通りよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:23.38,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217717,1223389}We don't know what traps, what strategies\Nlie ahead of us at the Interhigh.{NOTE:その他インターハイとも成れば、どんな伏兵が、がどんな作戦が待ち受けているか分からない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:28.06,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223389,1228060}Then there's Aoba High School, which participates in the tournament for the first time.{NOTE:原因無名だった青葉高校が大会へ出場することになったのも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:31.23,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228060,1231230}We only know they have\Na lot of outstanding spikers.{NOTE:ずば抜けた大型スパイかーがいるからなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:34.31,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231230,1234316}We don't lose in terms of outstanding players.{NOTE:あの、ずば抜けたのなら、ここにもいますけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:34.69,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234316,1234692}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:36.02,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234692,1236026}Hehe.{NOTE:ふふ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.77,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236902,1238779}What a faint, lonely smile.{NOTE:何て寂しそうな笑い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:41.32,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238779,1241323}Kozue never smiled like that before.{NOTE:こずえが一度も見せたこともない笑いだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:48.91,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247913,1248914}Ayuhara.{NOTE:鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.91,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248914,1250916}Don't look so sad.{NOTE:そんな寂しい顔をするのはいかん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:55.83,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252168,1255838}I know you're trying to forget Ichinose,\Nbut that's not enough to recover.{NOTE:一ノ瀬を忘れようとするだけでは決して立ち直ることはできんのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:57.71,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255838,1257715}Life and death are inseparable.{NOTE:人いうことは現実なのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:20:59.88,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257715,1259884}You have to accept and get over it.{NOTE:それを見守る。乗り越える。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:03.34,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259884,1263345}When you do so, you can make a big leap.{NOTE:その時こそお前は大きく飛躍できるのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:05.34,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263345,1265345}Get over it. Overcome death.{NOTE:乗り越えろ。死を乗り越えてくれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:08.30,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266599,1268309}It's a painful challenge.{NOTE:お前には辛い試練だろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:09.89,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268309,1269894}It's unbelievable.{NOTE:信じられんことだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:11.89,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269894,1271896}However!{NOTE:しかし！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:15.94,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271896,1275941}The vanishing attack isn't some romantic miracle.{NOTE:消えるアタックはロマンチック奇跡ではないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:17.40,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275941,1277401}Believe me.{NOTE:信じてくれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:19.57,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277401,1279570}Then complete it.{NOTE:そしてそれを完成させることだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:22.49,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1279570,1282490}That's what's going to make you recover.{NOTE:それがお前を立ち直らせることができる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:25.24,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282490,1285242}The vanishing attack is the way.{NOTE:そのための消えるアタックなのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:26.45,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285242,1286452}Attack.{NOTE:アタックだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:27.95,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286452,1287953}Attack it!{NOTE:アタックしてくれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:33.87,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1290956,1293876}Victory to Fujimi{NOTE:必勝富士見}
