Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:43.42,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1299673,1303427}Go! {\alpha&HFF&\t(1085,1085,\alpha&H00&)}Go! {\alpha&HFF&\t(2086,2086,\alpha&H00&)}Fu{\alpha&HFF&\t(2711,2711,\alpha&H00&)}ji{\alpha&HFF&\t(3295,3295,\alpha&H00&)}mi!{NOTE:フレ！フレ！富士見！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:47.68,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1305721,1307681}If you win, I'll date you!{NOTE:勝ったらデートしてやるぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:52.68,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309266,1312686}Hayakawa-kun! Ayuhara-san! Do your best!{NOTE:早川くん！鮎原さん！あのXXベストをつくせよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.68,0:21:55.18,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312686,1315189}You can count on us, Mitamura-kun.{NOTE:任しておいて、三田村くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:58.15,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1315189,1318150}Great! Good to see you cheered up!{NOTE:よし！元気成ったらこのXX忘れんなよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.15,0:21:59.65,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1318150,1319652}Mitamura-kun, it's all right already.{NOTE:三田村くん、もういいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:00.94,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319652,1320945}It's dangerous to run!{NOTE:走るは危ない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:02.15,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320945,1322154}I'll be fine!{NOTE:はっ、大丈夫さ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:04.44,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322154,1324448}Hayakawa-kun, don't lose to Kozue-san.{NOTE:早川くん！こずえさんに負けるなよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:06.03,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324448,1326033}Sure! I'll do my best!{NOTE:オッケー！任しておき。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:07.82,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327201,1327827}Oops!{NOTE:おっと！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:09.53,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328202,1329537}I told you!{NOTE:だから言ったでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.53,0:22:10.53,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329537,1330538}I'm fine!{NOTE:へ～、平気さ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:12.87,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331705,1332873}– Ah!\N– I knew it.{NOTE:—あっ。\\N—やっぱ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:30.26,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1349265,1350266}I'm so happy.{NOTE:よかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:31.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1350266,1351267}About?{NOTE:何が？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.26,0:22:33.72,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1351267,1353727}You need to ask?\NKozue, you look a lot better.{NOTE:何がって…こずえ元気でたじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.72,0:22:35.81,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1353727,1355813}Seems like Mitamura-kun's energy got to you.{NOTE:三田村くん目をパッチくるさせたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:43.15,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1358274,1363153}Looks like Tsutomu-san's ghost stopped haunting you, Kozue.{NOTE:どうやら努さんの幻は消えたらしいな、こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:46.49,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1364321,1366490}Weeping won't do us any good.{NOTE:メソメソしている場合じゃないもん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.49,0:22:48.74,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1366490,1368742}I'll give my best in the matches.{NOTE:試合に成ったらやるわよ、私。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:51.12,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1369159,1371120}That's the spirit. Keep it up!{NOTE:その意気。その意気よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.12,0:22:53.66,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1371120,1373664}Keep your head high, Attack No. 1.{NOTE:燃えろ、アタックナンバーワン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.46,0:23:03.21,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1381463,1383215}What should I do, Tsutomu-kun?{NOTE:どうしたらいいの、努くん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.42,0:23:13.43,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1388429,1393434}Vanishing attack… I can't even do double attack flawlessly.{NOTE:消えるアタックどころか…私ダブルアタックさえ満足にできないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.43,0:23:15.39,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1393434,1395392}I have to be strong before others, though.{NOTE:皆の前では強がってるけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.85,0:23:23.11,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1399857,1403110}I'm afraid I'll just freeze still on the court.{NOTE:コートに出ると手も足もすくんでしまうの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:31.70,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1406655,1411702}Kozue, I have no idea how to help you\Nother than pretending everything's fine.{NOTE:こずえ。苦しんでるあなたに私は知らん顔するしかないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.70,0:23:33.20,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1411702,1413203}Please, cheer up soon.{NOTE:何とか立ち直って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:35.08,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1413203,1415080}The tournament's just around the corner!{NOTE:試合は目の前なのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.74,0:23:38.33,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1415748,1418334}I must do what I have to do.{NOTE:それでも私はやらなければならない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:41.08,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1418334,1421086}That's the way, right? Tsutomu-kun!{NOTE:そうなんでしょう？努くん！}
