Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.73,0:24:08.19,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1440731,1448197}Kozue, tormented with memories of Tsutomu, is trying to pull herself together after his death.{NOTE:努の死を乗り越えて再起への決意をしたはずの梢の心の中はいまだうちもり努の面影を追い求めていたが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.19,0:24:13.91,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1448197,1453911}She meets again with her friends from\Nthe All-Japan team at the Interhigh tournament site.{NOTE:インターハイ大会場で偶然にもXXXの全日本ジュニアのチームメイト達と再会し…}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.91,0:24:16.58,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1453911,1456580}This time, they stand on the opposite sides of the court.{NOTE:互いに健闘を誓い合うのだった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.58,0:24:23.79,Alternative,Narrator,1,1,0,,{TIME:1456580,1463796}Kozue's determined to complete Tsutomu's gift to her,\Nthe vanishing attack. The first match begins.{NOTE:そして今こそ努が残してくれた消えるアタックを完成させようと決意しやがて第一線を迎えた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.79,0:24:26.63,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1463796,1466632}Please look forward to the next episode.{NOTE:次回「アタックナンバーワン」にご期待ください。}
